OL,7,FHe has pressed for a change in the
OL,8,Fplanning law after a landmark Supreme
OL,9,FCourt judgment for the protection of
OL,10,Fgreen spaces back in 2023.
OL,12,FIt ruled a statutory trust protecting
OL,13,Fland for public recreation remained in
OL,14,Fforce when sold by a local authority
OL,15,Funless a legally required consultation
OL,16,Fwas undertaken.
