OL,3,C'Legal shadow' over Wimbledon
OL,4,Cexpansion plans sparks 'get a grip'
OL,5,Cplea in Lords
OL,7,FLord O'Donnell said the decision in
OL,8,Fthe case of Day v Shropshire Council
OL,9,Fhad created uncertainty over
OL,10,Fdevelopment sites across the country,
OL,11,Fincluding Wimbledon, and stressed the
OL,12,Fneed for "legal clarity".
OL,14,FHe backed an amendment to the Planning
OL,15,Fand Infrastructure Bill, currently
OL,16,Fgoing through the House of Lords,
OL,17,Fwhich would release subsequent
OL,18,Fpurchasers of former public land from
OL,19,Fthe statutory trust provision.
