OL,5,Cplea in Lords
OL,7,FHe added: "The Day judgment has
OL,8,Fcreated significant delay and
OL,9,Funcertainty for Wimbledon's ability to
OL,10,Ftransform the land that has, for more
OL,11,Fthan a century, been a private
OL,12,Fmembers' golf club."
OL,14,FStressing the importance of the
OL,15,Fproposed expansion, the independent
OL,16,Fcrossbencher told the upper chamber:
OL,17,F"Wimbledon is a jewel in the crown of
OL,18,FBritish sport. The other grand slams
OL,19,Fare investing heavily in their
OL,20,Ffacilities and the fan experience.
