OL,7,F"One high-profile example ` although I
OL,8,Fstress it is only one of many ` is the
OL,9,Fcurrent proposal to expand the All
OL,10,FEngland Lawn Tennis Club's
OL,11,Finternationally renowned facilities at
OL,12,FWimbledon to include an adjacent
OL,13,Fformer private golf club site, the
OL,14,Fplanning permission for which was
OL,15,Frecently upheld by the High Court."
OL,17,FHe said his amendment would ensure
OL,18,F"bona fide purchasers of former open-
OL,19,Fspace land and their successes in
OL,20,Ftitle are free from the burden of a
OL,21,Fstatutory trust".
