OL,7,FBut raising her concern, Labour peer
OL,8,Fand former Environment Agency boss
OL,9,FBaroness Young of Old Scone said:
OL,10,F"This amendment has caused substantial
OL,11,Fconcern that it erodes the protection
OL,12,Fof green space and removes long-
OL,13,Fstanding public rights to green
OL,14,Fspaces, where the land is sold by
OL,15,Flocal authority, with or without
OL,16,Fconsultation."
OL,18,FLiberal Democrat Baroness Pinnock
OL,19,Fsaid: "You need to take people with
OL,20,Fyou on these big issues.
