OL,7,FShe added: "The Government recognise
OL,8,Fthat the issues relating to statutory
OL,9,Ftrusts need to be resolved.
OL,11,F"As a result, we are committed to
OL,12,Fworking at pace to find a solution
OL,13,Fthat works for developers and
OL,14,Fcouncils, while safeguarding the local
OL,15,Fspaces that are most valued by
OL,16,Fcommunities. We will seek to resolve
OL,17,Fthis issue in future legislation."
